===Etymology===
From {{etyl|frm}} {{term|Madagascar|lang=fr}}, of uncertain origin, but possibly from ''Madageiscar'', reputedly a corruption of [[w:Mogadishu|Mogadishu]] popularized by [[Marco Polo]].

